00:10:15.263 --> 00:10:18.383
Dewi Lakshmi
disebut Dhanalakshmi

00:10:19.463 --> 00:10:21.303
ketika dia memberi kekayaan.

00:10:21.583 --> 00:10:24.303
Dia dipanggil Dhanyalakshmi
ketika dia memberi hasil panen.

00:10:24.703 --> 00:10:27.983
Dia disebut Vidyalakshmi ketika
dia memberikan pengetahuan

00:10:29.943 --> 00:10:31.343
dan Veerlakshmi saat
dia memberi keberanian.

